      "message": "Because the field name is \"site\", lombok provides getSite & setSite, which does not meet the interface, which uses getSiteName & setSiteName.  Didn't want to rename the field to \"siteName\", because then we'd have to provide a DB-migration script to rename the columns.\n\nHowever, there's no compelling reason to leave the interface as it is, so I'll go ahead and rename it to \"site\" in there.",
